F. Coastal Mapping System using UAV
The coastal terrain changes sharply due to tide and ebb tide. For the safety, the government should build coastal safety map periodically and inform the changes of these terrain. For this purpose, the coastal mapping system using UAV is requested and hybrid aircraft is being developed collaborated with 3D mapping technology.

TABLE VII. SMALL UAV FOR COASTAL MAPPING

